description: Here's the trailer for my new documentary, Passing the Torch, featuring Jimmy Heath and the Tucson Jazz Institute Ellington Band, under the direction of Doug Tidaback. To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
title: Passing the Torch - Trailer
